Rebuild routed MoE gate/up as IQ1_S (or smallest viable) -- requires new weights

STATUS: open.  Biggest single quant lever, requires GGUF rebuild.

CONTEXT: feedback_moe_q8_gate_up_regresses.md shows MoE wall scales
linearly with weight bytes/elt at 99% MemUnitBusy ceiling.  Current
IQ2_XXS = 0.563 B/elt.  Production wall 46% of prefill from gate+up+down.
